<div class="helyx-configuration">
<div class="flexrow">
    <aside class="sidebar flexcol" style="height: 500px">
        <nav class="tabs" aria-label="Navigation">
            <a class="item category-tab active helyx-import-nav" id="helyx-nav-import" onclick="game.helyx.import_nav_tab('import');">
                Import
            </a>
            <a class="item category-tab helyx-import-nav" id="helyx-nav-pdf-list" onclick="game.helyx.import_nav_tab('pdf-list');">
                Supported PDFs
            </a>
            <a class="item category-tab helyx-import-nav" id="helyx-nav-faq" onclick="game.helyx.import_nav_tab('faq');">
                F.A.Q
            </a>
            <a class="item category-tab helyx-import-nav" id="helyx-nav-discord" onclick="game.helyx.import_nav_tab('discord');">
                Discord
            </a>
            <a class="item category-tab helyx-import-nav" id="helyx-nav-patreon" onclick="game.helyx.import_nav_tab('patreon');">
                Patreon
            </a>
        </nav>
    </aside>
    <form class="categories flexcol helyx-import-tab-space">
        <div class="scrollable">
            <section class="tab category helyx-import-tab active" id="helyx-tab-import">
                <h2 class="category-title">Import</h2>

                    <div class="form-group">        
                        <button id="helyx-import-pdf" class="helyx-inline" onclick="game.helyx.select_pdf();">Source PDF</button>
                        
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <p>
                            <b>Filename : </b>
                            <label id="helyx-imported-pdf-filename" class="helyx-inline helyx-import-filename" name="data">NOT SET</label>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="'form-group">
                        <h3>Warning !</h3>
                        <p>Although the module is tested every time it's released, bugs and errors exists.
                           Save yourself from despair : if you import an adventure into an existing world, 
                           backup this world before importing any PDF.   
                        </p> 
                    </div>

            </section>
            <section class="tab category helyx-import-tab hidden" id="helyx-tab-faq">
                {{> "modules/pf2-pdf-en-import/templates/exported/faq.hbs"}}
            </section>
            <section class="tab category helyx-import-tab hidden" id="helyx-tab-pdf-list">
                <h2 class="category-title">Supported PDFs</h2>
                {{> "modules/pf2-pdf-en-import/templates/exported/pdfList.hbs"}}
            </section>
            <section class="tab category helyx-import-tab hidden" id="helyx-tab-discord">
                <h2 class="category-title">Discord</h2>
                <p>There is a discord channel at <a href="https://discord.gg/XryTbnxWVq">https://discord.gg/XryTbnxWVq</a> for this import module.
                    You can use it to drop issues, get the latest news, submit ideas, or just say 'hi'.
                </p>
            </section>
            <section class="tab category helyx-import-tab hidden" id="helyx-tab-patreon">
                <p>A patreon is a way to support free softwares like this module. </p>

                <p>You can provide a few money to help buy new pdfs for new imports, or simply
                because you support free softwares like this one at the following patreon web page :
                    <br/> <a href="https://www.patreon.com/deidril">https://www.patreon.com/deidril</a> </p>

                <p>There is not special content for patreons. However, i may set up votes to decide
                of extra imported contents.</p>

                <p>I plan to continue to import PF2e stand-alone adventures and PFS adventures, and release new versions of
                this module for free.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </form>
</div></div>